[h4 
	" Gate of Beginning (たびだちのとびら)
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Required gate.
	$LF
	"I set the message speed to "8(slowest)".
	$LF
	"it's known to Japanese DQ RTA/TAS players that "the slowest is the fastest, when we press buttons repeatedly".
	$LF
	"It also helps for luck manipulation.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"No "HP 1 entertainment" at the battle of Healer, because every damage wastes about 30 frames.
	$LF
	"Befriended the strongest Healer(ホイミスライム) with AT 15. it saves some turns of later battles.
	$LF
]p
