[h4 
	" S Class Arena
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Required arena. Nothing to talk with 1st and 2nd battle.
	$LF
	"the 3rd battle annoys me so much as DonamerDragon had annoyed 5 years ago.
	$LF
	"Due to the fool AI, they don't attack Metabble（はぐれメタル）, when the other 2 monsters are alive.
	$LF
	"Metabble casts unavoidable magic every turn, unless we succeeded to cancel magic.
	$LF
	"Only when Roboster（キラーマシン） attacks before Metabble, Metabble re-thinks what to do and sometimes changes his action.
	$LF
	"After killing Roboster, my monsters had to kill Metal Drak（メタルドラゴン） while taking unavoidable damage from Metabbles.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Gate of Judgment （かがみのとびら）
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"I had planned to befriend Servant（まおうのつかい）, because he appears in unavoidable battle.
	$LF
	"but it was turned out that Servant can't do critical hit. so, i abandoned my plan and befriended Mimic（ミミック） as usual.
	$LF
